WEBVTT

00:09.677 --> 00:12.180
>> PREVIOUSLY
ON UNITED STATES OF TARA...

00:12.213 --> 00:14.415
>> I THINK IT MIGHT BE TIME FOR
YOU TO SEE ANOTHER THERAPIST.

00:14.448 --> 00:16.617
>> YOU'RE BREAKING UP WITH ME?

00:16.650 --> 00:18.386
>> WE NEED HER.
WHY'D SHE DO THAT?

00:18.419 --> 00:20.054
>> I MEAN,
YOU ARE A HANDFUL, TARA.

00:20.088 --> 00:21.822
>> WHAT DOES THAT MEAN?
>> THERE'S FOUR OF YOU.

00:21.855 --> 00:23.824
THAT'S NOT A RELATIONSHIP.
IT'S AN ORGY.

00:23.857 --> 00:25.793
>> I'M SORRY, MA'AM,
BUT IT'S YOUR SISTER.

00:25.826 --> 00:26.794
>> OF COURSE IT IS.

00:26.827 --> 00:28.629
TARA.
OH, MY GOD.

00:28.662 --> 00:29.630
>> [shouting]

00:29.663 --> 00:30.664
>> AAH!

00:30.698 --> 00:32.200
>> SOUNDS LIKE GIMME CAME OUT.

00:32.233 --> 00:33.601
>> HOW MANY TIMES
DO I HAVE TO TELL YOU?

00:33.634 --> 00:35.236
I DON'T KNOW SPIT
ABOUT THAT GIMME SPIT.

00:35.269 --> 00:37.438
>> WHAT THE HELL IS THAT?

00:37.471 --> 00:40.708
>> I SAW IT ON YOUR FRIDGE,
AND I-I COULDN'T RESIST.

00:40.741 --> 00:42.543
>> YOU STOLE A PICTURE
FROM ME?

00:42.576 --> 00:45.146
>> YOU KNOW, YOU MIGHT HAVE
GROUNDS FOR SEXUAL HARASSMENT.

00:45.179 --> 00:46.380
YOU SHOULD CALL H.R.

00:46.414 --> 00:47.815
>> TO MOTHER ISSUES.

00:47.848 --> 00:49.117
IT WASN'T BAD, WAS IT?

00:49.150 --> 00:50.484
>> WASN'T BAD AT ALL.

00:50.518 --> 00:52.353
>> YOU'RE MARSHALL'S B.F.

00:52.386 --> 00:54.522
>> I'M NOT ANYBODY'S B.F.

00:54.555 --> 00:57.125
MARSH, MAN, I AM--
I AM SO SORRY.

00:57.158 --> 00:58.259
>> MARSHALL.

00:58.292 --> 01:00.728
THAT WASN'T ME.
I WOULD NEVER--

01:01.629 --> 01:02.563
>> HEY.

01:03.864 --> 01:06.600
>> HELLO?
THE SHED'S ON FIRE!

01:06.634 --> 01:08.369
>> WHAT THE HELL?

01:08.402 --> 01:10.070
KATE, GET THAT OTHER HOSE!

01:13.874 --> 01:16.810
[contemplative music]

01:16.844 --> 01:20.581
*

01:20.614 --> 01:23.417
>> * OPEN UP THE SKY

01:23.451 --> 01:26.854
* THIS MESS IS GETTING HIGH

01:26.887 --> 01:31.592
* IT'S WINDY,
AND OUR FAMILY NEEDS A RIDE *

01:31.625 --> 01:33.761
